changeSet.author: Jordano
changeSet.sql: insert into relpessoacomarca (id_comarca, id_pessoa) select distinct c.ID, r.ID_PESSOA from REL_PESSOA_COMARCA_AUX r inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = r.id_comarca) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where (SELECT count(1) from relpessoacomarca p where p.id_comarca = c.id and p.id_pessoa = r.id_pessoa) = 0

insert into rel_comarca_tipojustica (comarca_id, tipojustica_id) select distinct c.id, t.id from comarca c, tipojustica t where (SELECT count(1) from rel_comarca_tipojustica r where r.comarca_id = c.id and r.tipojustica_id = t.id) = 0

insert into comarca_aud (id, id_aud, tipo_aud, descricao, metropolitana, fk_uf) select distinct c.ID, caux.id_aud, caux.TIPO_AUD, c.DESCRICAO, caux.METROPOLITANA, c.FK_UF from COMARCA_AUD_AUX caux inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = caux.id) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao))

update SOLICITACAO_LOG set IDCOMARCA = c.ID from SOLICITACAO_LOG s inner join SOLICITACAOLOG_AUX sa on (s.ID = sa.ID_SOLICITACAOLOG_AUX) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = sa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where s.IDCOMARCA is null

update SOLICITACAO_LOG_AUD set IDCOMARCA = c.id from SOLICITACAO_LOG_AUD s inner join SOLICITACAO_LOG_AUD_AUX sa on (s.ID = sa.ID_SOLICITACAO_LOG_AUD_AUX) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = sa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where s.IDCOMARCA is null

update REPARTICAO set FK_COMARCA = c.id from REPARTICAO r inner join REPARTICAO_AUX ra on (r.id = ra.ID) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = ra.FK_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where r.FK_COMARCA is null

update REPARTICAO_AUD set FK_COMARCA = c.id from REPARTICAO_AUD r inner join REPARTICAO_AUD_AUX ra on (r.id = ra.ID_REPARTICAO_AUD_AUX) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = ra.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where r.FK_COMARCA is null

update processo set FK_COMARCA = c.ID from PROCESSO p inner join PROCESSO_COMARCA_AUX pa on (p.ID = pa.ID_PROCESSO) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = pa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where p.FK_COMARCA is null

update processo_aud set FK_COMARCA = c.id from PROCESSO_AUD p inner join PROCESSO_AUD_AUX pa on (p.id = pa.ID_PROCESSO_AUD_AUX) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = pa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where p.FK_COMARCA is null

update foro set fk_comarca = c.ID from foro f inner join foro_aux fa on (fa.id = f.id) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = fa.FK_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where f.FK_COMARCA is null

update FORO_AUD set fk_comarca = c.ID from FORO_AUD f inner join FORO_AUD_AUX fa on (fa.ID_FORO_AUD_AUX = f.id) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = fa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where f.FK_COMARCA is null

update foro set fk_comarca = c.ID from foro f inner join foro_aux fa on (fa.id = f.id) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = fa.FK_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao) collate Latin1_General_CI_AI) where f.FK_COMARCA is null

changeSet.author: Jordano
changeSet.sql: UPDATE COMARCA SET DESCRICAO = trim(DESCRICAO)
delete from relpessoacomarca

insert into relpessoacomarca (id_comarca, id_pessoa) select distinct c.ID, r.ID_PESSOA from REL_PESSOA_COMARCA_AUX r inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = r.id_comarca) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)) where (SELECT count(1) from relpessoacomarca p where p.id_comarca = c.id and p.id_pessoa = r.id_pessoa) = 0
delete from rel_comarca_tipojustica

insert into rel_comarca_tipojustica (comarca_id, tipojustica_id) select distinct c.id, t.id from comarca c, tipojustica t where (SELECT count(1) from rel_comarca_tipojustica r where r.comarca_id = c.id and r.tipojustica_id = t.id) = 0
delete from comarca_aud;

insert into comarca_aud (id, id_aud, tipo_aud, descricao, metropolitana, fk_uf) select distinct c.ID, caux.id_aud, caux.TIPO_AUD, c.DESCRICAO, caux.METROPOLITANA, c.FK_UF from COMARCA_AUD_AUX caux inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = caux.id) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao))

UPDATE solicitacao_log as s SET IDCOMARCA = c.id FROM solicitacaolog_aux as sa, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE s.ID = sa.ID_SOLICITACAOLOG_AUX and ca.ID = sa.ID_COMARCA and upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)

UPDATE solicitacao_log_aud as s SET IDCOMARCA = c.id FROM solicitacao_log_aud_aux as sa, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE s.ID = sa.ID_SOLICITACAO_LOG_AUD_AUX and ca.ID = sa.ID_COMARCA and upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)
UPDATE reparticao as r SET fk_comarca = c.id FROM reparticao_aux as ra, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE r.id = ra.ID AND ca.ID = ra.FK_COMARCA AND upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)

UPDATE reparticao_aud as r SET fk_comarca = c.id FROM reparticao_aud_aux as ra, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE r.id = ra.ID_REPARTICAO_AUD_AUX AND ca.ID = ra.ID_COMARCA AND upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)

SELECT p.ID, P.FK_COMARCA as FK_COM_PROCESSO, C.ID as ID_COMARCA into tmp_comarca_atualiza FROM PROCESSO p inner join PROCESSO_COMARCA_AUX pa on (p.ID = pa.ID_PROCESSO) inner join comarca_aux ca on (ca.ID = pa.ID_COMARCA) inner join comarca c on (upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao));
UPDATE processo as p SET fk_comarca = t.id_comarca FROM tmp_comarca_atualiza as t WHERE p.id = t.id;

UPDATE processo_aud as p SET fk_comarca = c.id FROM processo_aud_aux as pa, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE p.id = pa.ID_PROCESSO_AUD_AUX AND ca.ID = pa.ID_COMARCA AND upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)
UPDATE foro as f SET fk_comarca = c.id FROM foro_aux as fa, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE fa.id = f.id AND ca.ID = fa.FK_COMARCA AND upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao)

UPDATE foro_aud as f SET fk_comarca = c.id FROM foro_aud_aux as fa, comarca_aux as ca, comarca as c WHERE fa.ID_FORO_AUD_AUX = f.id AND ca.ID = fa.ID_COMARCA AND upper(c.descricao) = upper(ca.descricao);
